&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in software development with a proven track record of architecting large-scale test automation initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert-level skills in software architecture, design patterns, and programming (TypeScript and/or C# preferred; Java/Python a plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert-level experience building frameworks from the ground up using multiple tools (Playwright preferred; Selenium, Cypress, or Appium acceptable).&lt;/li&gt;
